{"tag":"section","attrib":{"id":"iddb380b38-3a6f-11f1-8fa0-c065796a7f06","identifier":"/us/usc/t12/s361"},"text":null,"children":[{"tag":"num","attrib":{"value":"361"},"text":"§ 361.","children":[],"tail":null},{"tag":"heading","attrib":{},"text":" Bills receivable, bills of exchange, acceptances; regulations by Board of Governors","children":[],"tail":null},{"tag":"content","attrib":{},"text":"\n","children":[{"tag":"p","attrib":{},"text":"The discount and rediscount and the purchase and sale by any Federal reserve bank of any bills receivable and of domestic and foreign bills of exchange, and of acceptances authorized by this chapter, shall be subject to such restrictions, limitations, and regulations as may be imposed by the Board of Governors of the Federal Reserve System.","children":[],"tail":"\n"}],"tail":null},{"tag":"sourceCredit","attrib":{"id":"iddb380b39-3a6f-11f1-8fa0-c065796a7f06"},"text":"(","children":[{"tag":"ref","attrib":{"href":"/us/act/1913-12-23/ch6/s13"},"text":"Dec. 23, 1913, ch. 6, § 13","children":[],"tail":" (par.), "},{"tag":"ref","attrib":{"href":"/us/stat/38/264"},"text":"38 Stat. 264","children":[],"tail":"; "},{"tag":"ref","attrib":{"href":"/us/act/1916-09-07/ch461"},"text":"Sept. 7, 1916, ch. 461","children":[],"tail":", "},{"tag":"ref","attrib":{"href":"/us/stat/39/753"},"text":"39 Stat. 753","children":[],"tail":"; "},{"tag":"ref","attrib":{"href":"/us/act/1935-08-23/ch614/s203/a"},"text":"Aug. 23, 1935, ch. 614, § 203(a)","children":[],"tail":", "},{"tag":"ref","attrib":{"href":"/us/stat/49/704"},"text":"49 Stat. 704","children":[],"tail":".)"}],"tail":"\n"},{"tag":"notes","attrib":{"type":"uscNote","id":"iddb380b3a-3a6f-11f1-8fa0-c065796a7f06"},"text":"\n","children":[{"tag":"note","attrib":{"role":"crossHeading","topic":"editorialNotes","id":"iddb380b3b-3a6f-11f1-8fa0-c065796a7f06"},"text":null,"children":[{"tag":"heading","attrib":{},"text":null,"children":[{"tag":"b","attrib":{},"text":"Editorial Notes","children":[],"tail":null}],"tail":null}],"tail":"\n"},{"tag":"note","attrib":{"topic":"referencesInText","id":"iddb380b3c-3a6f-11f1-8fa0-c065796a7f06"},"text":"\n","children":[{"tag":"heading","attrib":{},"text":"References in Text","children":[],"tail":null},{"tag":"p","attrib":{},"text":"This chapter, referred to in text, was in the original “this Act”, meaning ","children":[{"tag":"ref","attrib":{"href":"/us/act/1913-12-23/ch6"},"text":"act Dec. 23, 1913, ch. 6","children":[],"tail":", "},{"tag":"ref","attrib":{"href":"/us/stat/38/251"},"text":"38 Stat. 251","children":[],"tail":", known as the Federal Reserve Act. For complete classification of this Act to the Code, see References in Text note set out under "},{"tag":"ref","attrib":{"href":"/us/usc/t12/s226"},"text":"section 226 of this title","children":[],"tail":" and Tables."}],"tail":"\n"}],"tail":"\n"},{"tag":"note","attrib":{"topic":"codification","id":"iddb380b3d-3a6f-11f1-8fa0-c065796a7f06"},"text":null,"children":[{"tag":"heading","attrib":{},"text":"Codification","children":[],"tail":"\n"},{"tag":"p","attrib":{},"text":"Section is based on the tenth par. of section 13 of act ","children":[{"tag":"date","attrib":{"date":"1913-12-23"},"text":"Dec. 23, 1913","children":[],"tail":", as amended. The tenth par. constituted the eighth par. of section 13 in 1916 ("},{"tag":"ref","attrib":{"href":"/us/stat/39/753"},"text":"39 Stat. 753","children":[],"tail":"), became the ninth par. in 1923 ("},{"tag":"ref","attrib":{"href":"/us/stat/42/1478"},"text":"42 Stat. 1478","children":[],"tail":"), and became the tenth par. in 1932 ("},{"tag":"ref","attrib":{"href":"/us/stat/47/715"},"text":"47 Stat. 715","children":[],"tail":"). For further details, see Codification notes under sections 342 to 344 of this title."}],"tail":"\n"}],"tail":"\n"},{"tag":"note","attrib":{"role":"crossHeading","topic":"statutoryNotes","id":"iddb380b3e-3a6f-11f1-8fa0-c065796a7f06"},"text":null,"children":[{"tag":"heading","attrib":{},"text":null,"children":[{"tag":"b","attrib":{},"text":"Statutory Notes and Related Subsidiaries","children":[],"tail":null}],"tail":null}],"tail":"\n"},{"tag":"note","attrib":{"topic":"changeOfName","id":"iddb380b3f-3a6f-11f1-8fa0-c065796a7f06"},"text":"\n","children":[{"tag":"heading","attrib":{},"text":"Change of Name","children":[],"tail":"\n"},{"tag":"p","attrib":{},"text":"Section 203(a) of act ","children":[{"tag":"date","attrib":{"date":"1935-08-23"},"text":"Aug. 23, 1935","children":[],"tail":", changed the name of the Federal Reserve Board to Board of Governors of the Federal Reserve System."}],"tail":"\n"}],"tail":"\n"}],"tail":"\n"}],"tail":null}
